Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷佐爾斯受到MS的襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的聯邦 竟然毫無警告就發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍部隊的MS中據說還有新型機 恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 他們是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PROUD的營救作戰還是延期…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 更應該提前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關眾多同志的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能失去他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聯繫營救部隊轉述作戰變更信息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聯邦政府 為消滅反政府勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已派遣政府直屬的治安維持部隊開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治安維持部隊將與聯邦保安局攜手\N更有效率的進行作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才司令部下令將我調往特別治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親眼見證也不失為一次良機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那支部隊中機密甚多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能探查內情自然求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是這個意思 那掛線了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪內金上校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何要事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 那件事考慮過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不急於一時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這樣 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長進不小嘛 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都來這裡半年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我新人了 叫沙慈．庫斯洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是艾迪．宮阪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為內通KATARON(希臘語純真)的嫌疑者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宮阪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也得一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手 我幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的新建航空巡洋艦 已朝L4出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王留美的報告沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要活著 必定會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種高重力下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不用機械
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別停手 R81
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想活命就少說多做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作 R81
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離 PROUD 2300
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散佈 維持通常濃度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑江中校 據說找到KATARON的艦船了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 先行部隊捕捉到並開始跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是朝PROUD去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型自動機器人(Automaton)的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部機體隨時待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始反政府勢力的掃蕩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD第一小隊 出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD 自動機器人搭載集裝箱 完成連接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各機能無異常  ALL GREEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基寧上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號機的阿勒威准尉是初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她感受一下戰場的氛圍就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 基寧小隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豈能就此屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在宇宙\N總有一天 能見到路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來不像當過軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是KATARON的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被捲進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你運氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時就知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只接到撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別丟下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡瓦爾多部隊 初步行動結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始營救作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介入第7區的重力系統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始介入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 正上方確認到MS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉嘉中尉 幹掉敵方部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒威准尉在原地待機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我按計劃進行新型機自動機器的性能實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標地點 集裝箱分離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始啟動新型自動機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 軍用自動機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對人兵器  A-LAWS幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是 剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈．庫斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:11:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號機 判斷得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 為什麼你會在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和當初絲毫未變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E探測器反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂和我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰要這種世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴上頭盔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 那機影是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那GN粒子是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自動機器人的數量在減少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 上面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXIA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM EXIA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 為什麼你會是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何事到如今還出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你們的行徑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要加以驅逐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM也不過是5年前的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是AHEAD的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號機 掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我們自己上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾多戰友死於你手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天讓我 報仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的時代結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GN FIELD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背上有臉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答 三號機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在打探A-LAWS的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞．艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛迪先生發現EXIA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 果然在PROUD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王小姐的情報好準
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會吃驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見到拉塞先生時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算有機會試用EXIA的太陽爐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PROUD出現了GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須感謝他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於能救出倖存的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是次好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能會成為武力介入的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們與我們志同道合 席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四年不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣質變化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你卻幾乎毫無改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和當時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常被人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台GUNDAM 是天人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英 你是駕駛GUNDAM的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈．庫斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你從5年前就開始武力介入？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎 你們做的事害死多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你們害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的人都到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家人和親屬被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的親姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也因為天人的牽連 被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她們還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會受到GUNDAM的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 這樣我們就更有必要存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙會進A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯．阿勒威  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你也有了戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲 有人求見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊和新GUNDAM發生接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還未確認GUNDAM是否隸屬天人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從未對自己是處女座感到如此高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前來迎接索瑪．比利斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下是第五MS中隊所屬\N安德雷．史米盧佐夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德雷 什麼時候加入A-LAWS的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有義務回答你 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 瑟爾蓋．史米盧佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父…親？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有開槍打剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的話就和你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝剎那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不帶你來這裡的話
